review_blob: Great beer. Strong chocolate overtones, with sweet finish. Great beer for the end of the day. Thick and dark in the glass. Its like an Imperial stout should be.
beer_name: 4 Hands Brewers Choice Imperial Milk Stout

review_blob: The best thing about this beer is the smell, plum and chocolate. Its a little thinner than I thought it would be, not a bad thing. A slight bitter finish and a little on the lighter finish for a IS.

Velvet texture, started a little peppery, but could taste the coffee and chocolate overtones. Definitely agree that it has a bitter finish. 

Nice beer.
beer_name: Evil Twin I Love You With My Stout
